{
  "texts": [
    "It provides a score ranging from 0 to 1, where 1 indicates a perfect match and 0 indicates no match at all.Dice = 2 × TP 2 × TP + FP + FN.",
    "(4)S-measure (S α).",
    "Structure measure [99] evaluates the structural similarity of segmentation results.S α = α • S O + (1 -α) • S R,( 5)where S O represents the object similarity, which measures the overlap between the segmentation result and the ground truth target.",
    "S R represents the region similarity, which assesses the structural similarity between the segmentation result and the ground truth target.",
    "The parameter α is used to balance the weights between these two measures."
  ]
}